data.description: Come see this single level home in the Foothills, Wingfield Springs. Conveniently located near sports fields, golf, shopping, schools and restaurants. The home has a nice open kitchen, dining and living area. Outside is nicely landscaped with a paved patio and mature trees. Great for relaxing or entertaining. Home offers three bedrooms and three bathrooms providing space and privacy along with a three car garage to park your vehicles.
